-- Vestas Wins 50-Megawatt China Order From Hanas New Energy
-- B y   A l e x   M o r a l e s
-- 2013-08-13T08:54:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-13/vestas-wins-50-megawatt-china-order-from-hanas-new-energy.html
Vestas Wind Systems A/S (VWS)  won a 50-megawatt wind-turbine order from  China ’s Hanas New Energy.  The order for 25 V90 2-megawatt turbines is the third by
Hanas, a natural gas supplier in China’s Ningxia Hui Autonomous
Region, Vestas said today in a  statement  on its website. The
Chinese company already has 150 megawatts of Vestas turbines in
operation, with a further 50 megawatts under construction.  The order includes turbines, towers and a two-year service
agreement, with delivery of the first machine expected this
quarter, Vestas said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Morales in London at 
